title: J.C - Jam: BBQ Final 2016   Part(2/2)
description:
The BBQ Game jam is about creating a game in 24 hours with fun and skills people to finish on a super good barbecue.
It takes place in Luxembourg every year at the end of summer holiday.

This video is the presentation of the projects at then end of it.
